        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 12 at 1:43PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 141 PM PDT, the public reported a strong thunderstorm near Minam,
or 24 miles northeast of La Grande, moving northeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Pea size hail.

SOURCE...Public.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Minam.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
